ARTICLE III — EIGHT ABSOLUTE PROHIBITIONS

  Without the prior express written authorization of the Author, the
  following acts are absolutely prohibited. These prohibitions apply
  regardless of purpose, intent, jurisdiction, medium, or method:

  3.1  REPRODUCTION — No person or entity may copy, clone, fork,
       download, cache, screenshot, photograph, transcribe, or
       otherwise reproduce the Software or any portion thereof.

  3.2  DISTRIBUTION — No person or entity may distribute, share,
       transmit, publish, republish, mirror, host, serve, relay, or
