       any third party by any means.

  3.3  MODIFICATION — No person or entity may modify, alter, adapt,
       translate, annotate, extend, refactor, rewrite, or create any
       derivative work based upon the Software.

  3.4  REVERSE ENGINEERING — No person or entity may reverse engineer,
       decompile, disassemble, analyze, inspect, probe, trace, debug,
       or otherwise attempt to discover the source code, algorithms,
       mathematical formulations, architectural patterns, data
       structures, or trade secrets of the Software.

  3.5  COMMERCIAL USE — No person or entity may use the Software or
       any portion thereof for any commercial purpose, including but
       not limited to selling, licensing, leasing, offering as a
       service, incorporating into a product, or deriving revenue in
       any form.

  3.6  AI TRAINING — No person, entity, model, agent, crawler, spider,
       scraper, indexer, or automated system may use the Software or
       any portion thereof — including source code, documentation,
